---
import PageLayout from "../layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout
  title="NDMDs — Neurodiversity in Medicine Society"
  description="Private space for ND/NDq Unimelb MD students. UMMSS-affiliated; peer support, advocacy, and community for neurodivergent medical students."
>
  <section
    class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-lime/35 via-white to-brand-cyan/25"
    aria-labelledby="hero-heading"
  >
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24">
      <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] lg:items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wide text-brand-teal/80">
            University of Melbourne · Doctor of Medicine
          </p>
          <h1
            id="hero-heading"
            class="mt-3 text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight text-brand-teal sm:text-5xl"
          >
            A welcoming space for neurodivergent medical students
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-5 max-w-xl text-lg text-brand-teal/90">
            We host a private community for <abbr title="neurodivergent">ND</abbr> and <abbr
              title="neurodivergent-questioning">NDq</abbr
            >
            Unimelb MD students — whether you are diagnosed, identifying, or still
            figuring things out. Official UMMSS club; GSA affiliation in progress.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a
              href="/contact/"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-teal px-6 py-3 text-base font-bold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:bg-brand-teal-muted focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-brand-teal"
              >Join the community</a
            >
            <a
              href="/about/"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-brand-teal/30 bg-white px-6 py-3 text-base font-bold text-brand-teal transition hover:border-brand-teal/50 hover:bg-brand-surface focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-brand-teal"
              >Our vision</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
          <img
            src="/ndmds-logo.png"
            alt="NDMDs circular logo with a stylised brain and society name"
            width="240"
            height="240"
            class="h-56 w-56 drop-shadow-md sm:h-64 sm:w-64"
            loading="eager"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section
    class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 sm:py-16"
    aria-labelledby="mission-heading"
  >
    <h2
      id="mission-heading"
      class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-brand-teal sm:text-3xl"
    >
      What we do
    </h2>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg text-brand-teal/90">
      We celebrate neurodiversity in medicine by sharing experiences, busting myths, and
      pooling resources — online and in person. We create{" "}
      <strong class="font-bold text-brand-teal">safe spaces</strong>, build{" "}
      <strong class="font-bold text-brand-teal">peer support</strong>, and promote{" "}
      <strong class="font-bold text-brand-teal">self-knowledge</strong> for members and
      learning for allies. Each year we aim for{" "}
      <strong class="font-bold text-brand-teal">at least two events</strong>: one for
      members only, and one that welcomes Melbourne Medical School partners for
      education and allyship.
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-8 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <li
        class="rounded-2xl border border-brand-teal/10 bg-brand-surface p-5 shadow-sm"
      >
        <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-teal">Peer support</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-brand-teal/85">
          Connect with others who understand the joys and challenges of medicine while
          living neurodivergence in your own way — including seeing the heterogeneity of
          our community.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li
        class="rounded-2xl border border-brand-teal/10 bg-brand-surface p-5 shadow-sm"
      >
        <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-teal">Advocacy</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-brand-teal/85">
          We speak up for how medical education is delivered and for neurodiverse
          patients in the MD curriculum.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li
        class="rounded-2xl border border-brand-teal/10 bg-brand-surface p-5 shadow-sm sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1"
      >
        <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-teal">Resources</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-brand-teal/85">
          University services, wellbeing links, and tools students have found helpful —
          curated on our resources page.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/resources/"
          class="mt-3 inline-flex font-semibold text-brand-teal underline decoration-brand-cyan underline-offset-2 hover:decoration-brand-teal"
          >Browse resources</a
        >
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section
    class="border-t border-brand-teal/10 bg-brand-surface"
    aria-labelledby="cta-heading"
  >
    <div
      class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-14 text-center sm:px-6 sm:py-16"
    >
      <h2 id="cta-heading" class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-brand-teal">
        Get involved
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-2xl text-lg text-brand-teal/90">
        Whether you want to come to an event, ask a question, or simply know you are not
        alone — we would love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact/"
        class="mt-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-teal px-8 py-3.5 text-base font-bold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:bg-brand-teal-muted focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-brand-teal"
        >Contact us</a
      >
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
